{"tid":2090374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方：市民報案黃店文宣或違國安法  到場勸喻開店前清理","createTime":"2020-07-02T06:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T07:30:49.000Z","uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"855fe44bb1ffad45325f7f6511bb61d56f8215fb","tid":2090374,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:38:27.000Z","msg":"「港區國安法」實施第二日，有警員今早到位於筲箕灣的黃店「壹碗壹麵」勸喻店主清走店內文宣，否則有可能觸犯國安法。據到場了解的「香港中小企食店聯盟」召集人林瑞華店方說法，警員並沒有明確指出是違反甚麼章節，只稱收到市民報警遂到場了解。<br />\n<br />\n「壹碗壹碟」今早 11 時許在 Facebook 貼文指，筲箕灣店今日突發休業「直至另行通知」。中午 12 時許，店鋪閘門拉上，店主及店員用工具清走店內文宣，店內彌漫天拿水味，店主婉拒記者訪問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/稱接市民報案-警到筲箕灣黃店指文宣或違國安法-壹碗壹碟-緊急清理/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A8%B1%E6%8E%A5%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%A0%B1%E6%A1%88-%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%B0%E7%AD%B2%E7%AE%95%E7%81%A3%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E6%8C%87%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3%E6%88%96%E9%81%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E5%A3%B9%E7%A2%97%E5%A3%B9%E7%A2%9F-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8BR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=e0a636c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A8%B1%E6%8E%A5%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%A0%B1%E6%A1%88-%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%B0%E7%AD%B2%E7%AE%95%E7%81%A3%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E6%8C%87%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3%E6%88%96%E9%81%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E5%A3%B9%E7%A2%97%E5%A3%B9%E7%A2%9F-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%2F&h=ab3fbc5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/稱接市民報案-警到筲箕灣黃店指文宣或違國安法-壹碗壹碟-緊急清理/</a>"},{"pid":"1eacccc4e68ed42bc83746f5cb6ff8a0d625efd1","tid":2090374,"uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:40:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>如果你有90秒，睇一睇琴日警察嘅策略同納粹有咩分別：<br />\n</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xbFFY9CPduw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxbFFY9CPduw&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8BR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=a8770419\" targe